com.datecs.api.printer
Interface ProtocolAdapter.ChannelListener

Enclosing class:
ProtocolAdapter
public static interface ProtocolAdapter.ChannelListener

Interface definition for a callbacks to be invoked when status event occurs in ProtocolAdapter.Channel. The callback is called in new thread environment.

onLowBattery

void onLowBattery(boolean state)
This callback is invoked when printer battery is low.

The event may occur only on CHANNEL_PRINTER.

Parameters:
state - indicates whether the battery level is low or not.
